msgid "If you're capturing an incident trace, log payload, or external response in a test fixture: redact and anonymize before committing. Real session IDs, real user IDs, real hostnames, and real auth tokens all need to go through a scrubbing pass first. The redacted version is what ships; the original stays out of git."
