msgid "Skills are plain Markdown with YAML frontmatter. Their `description` field is what Claude Code uses to decide when to trigger them — be specific and include concrete trigger phrases (`\"review 1234\"`, `\"triage issues\"`, etc.). Use `skill-creator` to edit them; it enforces the structure and helps run evals to measure trigger accuracy."
