msgid "`ChannelKind`, `ToolKind`, `CronKind`, `MemoryKind`, and the four `ProviderKind` sub-enums (`ModelProviderKind`, `TtsProviderKind`, `TranscriptionProviderKind`, `TunnelProviderKind`) are all closed. The variant's snake_case form via `strum::IntoStaticStr` is the canonical `<type>` portion of the `<type>.<alias>` composite. Adding a new implementation: extend the relevant `Kind` enum, that's it."
